  <title>INFORMATION TECHNOLOGY TECHNICIAN  - (SEACMEQ) (Re-advertisement)</title>
  <link>https://www.ub.bw/connect/job-opportunities/information-technology-technician-seacmeq-re-advertisement</link>
  <description>&lt;span class="field field--name-title field--type-string field--label-hidden"&gt;INFORMATION TECHNOLOGY TECHNICIAN  - (SEACMEQ) (Re-advertisement)&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;span class="field field--name-uid field--type-entity-reference field--label-hidden"&gt;&lt;a title="View user profile." href="https://www.ub.bw/user/2371" lang="" about="https://www.ub.bw/user/2371" typeof="schema:Person" property="schema:name" datatype="" class="username" xml:lang=""&gt;mfetane&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/span&gt;
